### CSS Forms

Style form elements for better usability and appearance.

---

### Input Fields

```css
input[type="text"],
input[type="email"],
input[type="password"],
textarea,
select {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-family: inherit;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
}

input:focus,
textarea:focus,
select:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: #3498db;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.2);
}
```

---

### Labels

```css
label {
  display: block;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #333;
}
```

---

### Input States

```css
/* Valid */
input:valid {
  border-color: #2ecc71;
}

/* Invalid */
input:invalid {
  border-color: #e74c3c;
}

/* Required */
input:required {
  border-left: 3px solid #f39c12;
}

/* Disabled */
input:disabled {
  background: #f5f5f5;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Placeholder */
input::placeholder {
  color: #999;
}
```

---

### Textarea

```css
textarea {
  min-height: 120px;
  resize: vertical;  /* Allow vertical resize only */
}
```

---

### Select Dropdown

```css
select {
  appearance: none;         /* Remove default arrow */
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,...");
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-position: right 12px center;
  background-size: 16px;
  padding-right: 40px;
}
```

---

### Checkboxes & Radios

```css
/* Custom checkbox */
input[type="checkbox"] {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  accent-color: #3498db;
}

/* Custom radio */
input[type="radio"] {
  accent-color: #3498db;
}
```

---

### Form Layout

```css
.form-group {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.form-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.form-error {
  color: #e74c3c;
  font-size: 13px;
  margin-top: 5px;
}
```

> **Best Practice:** Use `font-size: 16px` on inputs to prevent iOS zoom on focus. Always style `:focus` state.
